          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃瑶池金母是也。今有长寿星君，千秋华诞之日。已曾命方朔，约请众仙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去祝寿。这样时候，不见到来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东方朔上，嗽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金母在上，方朔稽首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方朔免礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣寿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我命你约请众仙，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众仙俱已请下。顷刻就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到时禀我知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蟠桃果树三千岁，海屋添筹不记时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿酒频斟歌寿曲，年年福寿与天齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。金母、东方朔同下。吹打住。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大仙请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑 （内同白） 请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑 （内同新水令） 捧蟠桃鲜果，庆千秋，老寿星，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑 （同新水令） 献花祝寿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瑞霭遍珠楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿同瑶升平久，寿同瑶升平久。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉钟离。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五岳冠横驾鹤飞，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕洞宾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕洞宾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕洞宾",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千百年前进士身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张果老",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张果老。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张果老",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒骑驴儿遍琼岛，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蓝采和",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蓝采和。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蓝采和",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉板轻敲踏道歌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹国舅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹国舅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹国舅",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不受金章与紫绶，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李铁拐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李铁拐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脚踏浮萍过大海。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩湘子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩湘子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩湘子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "简板相随不记齿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "何仙姑",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何仙姑",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笟篱天地在悬壶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大仙请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金母相召，只得向前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东方朔上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大仙到齐了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到齐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金母有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。金母上。吹打住。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启上金母：众仙俱已到齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道。有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东方朔",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大仙，金母有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑同进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金母在上，我等稽首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众仙少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣寿。请问金母，相召我等，有何见谕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有长寿星君，千秋华诞之日。特邀众仙到此，一同前去祝寿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既如此，一同驾云前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同驻马听） 鸾鹤遨游，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千风万岫归苍秀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笙萧列锦讴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恰似天台山下去寻刘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见那桃园洞口波声流。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早向那白云峰，齐庆祝千年叟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "向那白云峰，齐庆祝千年叟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已到寿筵前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众仙各将寿物献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小仙呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 汉钟离遥献紫琼勾，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吕洞宾 （折桂令） 吕洞宾满捧着玉液金瓯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张果老 （折桂令） 张果老擎着千岁烛，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蓝采和 （折桂令） 蓝采和慢舞着长衫袖。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹国舅 （折桂令） 捧寿面的曹国舅，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李铁拐 （折桂令） 岳孔目将铁拐住，祝千秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩湘子 （折桂令） 献牡丹的韩湘子，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑 （折桂令） 进灵龟的何仙姑，在笟篱内游。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问金母，将何物为寿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有蟠桃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白猿何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鹤、鹿、寿物随白猿同上。白猿跳，捧桃放生。鹤、鹿、寿物、白猿同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同雁儿落） 将仙桃仙果收，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把仙箓仙丹授。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听仙乐、仙音奏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "引仙鹿到丹丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听仙家、仙女讴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙座下嬉游。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙苑内清幽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万年松千岁竹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金母 （雁儿落） 向金盘取一棵寿果，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺将这蟠桃刊为首。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同祝你寿筵前，般般有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何仙姑 （同雁儿落） 寿筵前，般般有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "汉钟离、吕洞宾、张果老、蓝采和、曹国舅、李铁拐、韩湘子、何仙姑",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祝寿已毕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众仙就此拜寿者。"
        },
        {
